Document R package.

Usage:
  document.R [--before_code=<"stop"|"stash"|"commit">] [--after_code=<"stop"|"commit">]

Options:
  --before_code=<"stash"|"commit"> passed to `ghactions::check_clean_tree()`. Otherwise throws an error.
  --after_code=<"commit"> passed to `ghactions::auto_commit()`. Otherwise throws an error.
